OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBand
OL,6,Fof rain clears south early Monday,
OL,7,Ffollowed by brighter spells. Further
OL,8,Frain overnight and Tuesday morning,
OL,9,Fwith showers following. Wednesday
OL,10,Fbreezy with widespread heavy showers,
OL,11,Fpossibly thundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
